raw_text: Balcony 1 is located on far south side of the plan, extended little bit off the entire plan with kitchen on north, with 10 feet length and 5 feet breath. Balcony 2 is located on far north side of the plan, extended little bit off the entire plan, with master on south side, total area is 10 x 5 feet. exact center on west side, surrounded by master on north and living east, 5 x5 feet. The common room is located on north east corner, with master on west side and living on south side, total area of cover is 10 x 15 feet.
